NUMERICALLY 'CLOSE' VALUES AND THEN DETERMINES WHETHER THE                      
IMPLEMENTATION CAN DISTINGUISH BETWEEN THEN OR IF THEY ARE                      
TREATED AS EQUAL.                                                               
                                                                                
